# 9. UVM Migration Roadmap

Only after project signoff.

Convert:

```
APB BFM
    ↓
UVM Driver

APB Monitor
    ↓
UVM Monitor

Transaction
    ↓
Sequence Item

Tests
    ↓
Sequences

Scoreboard
    ↓
UVM Scoreboard

Registers
    ↓
UVM RAL
```

Objective:

```
Understand UVM through an already working environment.
```

---

# 10. Final Learning Outcomes

Upon completion the engineer shall understand:

✓ Register Verification

✓ APB Protocol

✓ AXI-Lite Protocol

✓ Bus Functional Models

✓ Monitors

✓ Scoreboards

✓ Functional Coverage

✓ Assertions

✓ Interrupt Verification

✓ Address Decoding

✓ Integration Verification

✓ SoC Verification

✓ UVM Migration

End of Document
